==German==
===Pronunciation===
/ʃarf/
===Etymology===
Old High German ''scar(p)f'', akin to Old Saxon ''skarp'', compare Dutch [[scherp]]
===Adjective===
'''scharf''' (schärfer, schärfst)
# [[sharp]] (knife, intellect)
# [[hot]] (spicy)
# [[nipping]]
